# Environment Variables for Production Deployment

## Required Environment Variables

### Database (Automatically set by Vercel Postgres)
# These are automatically populated when you add Vercel Postgres storage
# No manual configuration needed!
POSTGRES_URL=""
POSTGRES_PRISMA_URL=""
POSTGRES_URL_NO_SSL=""
POSTGRES_URL_NON_POOLING=""
POSTGRES_USER=""
POSTGRES_HOST=""
POSTGRES_PASSWORD=""
POSTGRES_DATABASE=""

## Optional Environment Variables

### Google Gemini AI (Recommended)
# For AI-enhanced features:
# - Smart column detection in uploaded files
# - Intelligent transaction categorization
# - Personalized financial insights
# Get your free API key at: https://makersuite.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY="your-gemini-api-key-here"

### Next.js Configuration
# NODE_ENV is automatically set by Vercel
# NODE_ENV="production"

